  "gwSpecs": {
    "description": "The Showtec Compact Par 7 Tri is a compact 7x 3 watt RGB LED Par with double bracket for easy floor positioning, suitable for indoor venues. It has a 40° fixed beam angle and features a 0 - 100 % dimmer and 0 - 20 Hz strobe function, perfectly suitable for short-throw colour mixing. The Compact Par 7 Tri can be controlled manually, via DMX and Master/Slave in either Manual, Auto run, or Sound-controlled mode with many available built-in programs. Its design fits in every setting with either black and grey housing.",
